message.body: UM have you seen maroon 5s music vid for sugar?

Also, my TA totally thinks I'm crazy. We got new locks for our lockers in chem lab. I preceded to throw out the box without writing the number combo. Hahahah

What in the world...I was talking to mommy about the classes I have to take and everything. Woman be crazy, she doesn't understand why I have to take summer classes. She said "you have to do this and then another 3.5 years at jefferson?" I said "yeah, or I could not go to nursing school at all." That shut her up real fast.
Hahaha
